    <string name="hacknovation_is_a_flagship_36_hour_non_stop_innovation_hackathon_conducted_at_giet_university_bringing_together_some_of_the_brightest_young_minds_from_across_the_region_n_nwith_80_teams_and_200_participants_hacknovation_fosters_creativity_collaboration_and_real_world_problem_solving_the_event_provides_a_flexible_innovation_environment_where_students_transform_ideas_into_impactful_solutions_across_domains_like_ai_web_mobile_cybersecurity_iot_and_emerging_technologies_n_nparticipants_engage_in_intense_brainstorming_expert_mentoring_sessions_technical_workshops_and_final_project_presentations_before_an_experienced_jury_panel_n_norganized_under_the_guidance_of_giet_university_hacknovation_aims_to_inspire_the_next_generation_of_innovators_and_entrepreneurs">Hacknovation is a flagship 36-hour non-stop innovation hackathon conducted at GIET University, bringing together some of the brightest young minds from across the region.\n\nWith 80+ teams and 200+ participants, Hacknovation fosters creativity, collaboration, and real-world problem solving. The event provides a flexible innovation environment where students transform ideas into impactful solutions across domains like AI, Web, Mobile, Cybersecurity, IoT, and Emerging Technologies.\n\nParticipants engage in intense brainstorming, expert mentoring sessions, technical workshops, and final project presentations before an experienced jury panel.\n\nOrganized under the guidance of GIET University, Hacknovation aims to inspire the next generation of innovators and entrepreneurs.</string>
